{"tid":2444633,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"whey乳清蛋白交流區(6)","createTime":"2021-03-13T03:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T09:41:56.000Z","uid":212473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"aa47618d7936a1006886704716e8c6a0a3d159a2","tid":2444633,"uid":212473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T03:36:34.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家留低飲過cp值高嘅whey<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中過伏嘅都可以講低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有買開嘅可以順便報個價方便巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩問嘅都歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預咗會有人問所以講定先，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhey只係一種補充劑，並唔係咩神奇藥，只要你一日嘅蛋白質攝取不足就可以飲。<br />\n<br />\n但點解咁多做尖嘅師兄會飲？<br />\n因為whey係一個方便、經濟嘅蛋白質來源，而蛋白質正正就起收復肌肉上擔當住一個重要角色。成件事就只係咁單純<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外起市面上普遍買左嘅whey都會分兩種<br />\n<br />\n第1種：whey protein<br />\n佢Marco嘅數字會稍微高少少，但相對價錢會平啲，消化吸收嘅時間都會耐少少。<br />\n<br />\n第2種: Whey isolate <br />\n因為佢過慮得比較清，所以Marco會靚仔啲，當然價錢都會貴啲，但吸收消化就快好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但基本上只要你唔係有咩特別目的 e.g.比賽/體質對乳糖特別敏感其實都唔洗飲到咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩唔明歡迎再問，亦歡迎師兄們幫手解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d633b35498bbb8a975e7fea7eee908f5eec8285a","tid":2444633,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T03:38:38.000Z","msg":"on士多啤梨味如何?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cecd13c8ee5fb387514493d459fd3d721811fb","tid":2444633,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T21:03:55.000Z","msg":"自家蛋白<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cff9e56f5d97189557641f1be19ce5f2fed4ac",